title: Arose gabw nwngni sigangao
lyrics:
Arose gabw nwngni sigangao -2
Gaswi jwngni nangou khou
Nwng gaswi mithijwbgou
“O . . . swrgw Bifa jwngni”-2 -2
(A)
Anldainai subungni Bifa nwngw
Menglinai subungni laokhar nwngw -2
Jiu arw jiu, Rajani raja, Gwthar fwrni gwthar -2
(B)
Gwthar khwmsalini gudi nwngw
Gwmanai subungni lama nwngw -2
Bifa-Bisa, Gwthar jiu jwng
Saselo Isor Nwng-2
